535
00:27:24.320 --> 00:27:25.600
Mina damer och herrar.

536
00:27:25.680 --> 00:27:26.960
Objekt 12-46.

537
00:27:27.040 --> 00:27:29.080
TTV Agrotron 50k-motorn.

538
